👉 Quick Quiz : Write a JAVA program to print the elements of an array in reverse order.

CODE : 

public class Arrays {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int marks[] = {34, 45, 56, 67, 89};
        int x = marks.length;
        for (int i = x-1; i >= 0; i--) {
            System.out.println(marks[i]);
        }
    }
}

OUTPUT :

89
67
56
45
34

